CONTRIBUTING
------------

# install Dist::Zilla
$ cpanm Dist::Zilla

# clone the repo
$ git clone https://github.com/book/Devel-TraceUse.git
$ cd Devel-TraceUse

# install author dependencies if you want to build the package and run the tests:
$ dzil listdeps --author --missing | cpanm
$ dzil authordeps --missing | cpanm

# install usage dependencies
$ dzil listdeps | cpanm

# run tests against built code:
$ dzil test

# create a bundle of built code:
$ dzil build
# creates Devel-Trace-2.096 and Devel-Trace-2.096.tar.gz
